data.description: This 2 year old Josselyn Homes built 4 bedroom 3 bath home features a miraculous pond view on a large estate sized lot. Walk inside to a split floor plan with open island kitchen, granite counter tops, custom cabinetry & smudge resistant Bosch stainless appliances with separate cooktop and wall oven . The master suite boasts dual walk in closets, an elegant master bath with double vanity, soaker tub & tile walk-in shower. A must see home offering many upgrades with custom wood closet shelving throughout, LED lighting, wood look tile flooring & 3 car garage!
